# Dependencies
**/node_modules
**/venv
**/venv_temp
**/__pycache__
**/.vite

# Build artifacts
**/dist
**/*.pyc
**/.pytest_cache

# Secrets (never bake into images)
**/.env
**/secrets.env
**/*.log

# Version control
**/.git
**/.gitignore

# IDE
**/.vscode
**/.idea

# Documentation
**/*.md
**/docs
**/files

# Test files
**/test_*.py
**/verify_*.py
**/backtest_*.py
**/debug_*.py
**/check_*.py
**/*.log
**/*.txt

# Docker files (don't copy docker files into images)
docker-compose.yml
docker.env.template
.dockerignore
